ConfigurationSummaryReportForm is a Form
    Layout
        header4 of "<Name>"
            underline color of black
        visible when (Description entered)
            paragraph
                Description
                    no label
        paragraph
            visible when (InViewContext)
                BusinessView
            EntityType
        paragraph
            Status
                raise red alert when (Status.Invalid)
                    mouse over text is "Invalid"
                raise yellow alert when (Status.Inactive)
                    mouse over text is "Inactive"
            DerivedLastChange
                label is "Audit"
                display as tag
                    color of blue
        single column
            blank line
